content:
Adjust details and assignments for individual units, areas, and boundaries when you edit them directly from the legend in Territory Planning.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: To update territory, assignment, and attribute details directly on the legend, hover over the element that you want to update. Then click Edit.

Some updates, such as calculations, appear after you reload the focus or the legend.
title: Editing Territory Details in Salesforce
